section.home-strengths
    .container
        .home-section-header
            p.home-section-label(data-i18n='strengths.kicker', data-en='Why CHX', data-zh='为什么选择我们') Why CHX
            h2.home-section-title(data-i18n='strengths.title', data-en='What Sets Us Apart', data-zh='我们的核心竞争力') What Sets Us Apart
            p.home-section-sub(data-i18n='strengths.sub', data-en='Built on two decades of industry experience, supply chain depth, and a commitment to practical solutions.', data-zh='二十年行业积累、完善的供应链体系与以实际工况为导向的解决方案能力。') Built on two decades of industry experience, supply chain depth, and a commitment to practical solutions.
        .home-strengths-grid
            .home-strength-item
                .home-strength-icon
                    i.fa-solid.fa-link(aria-hidden='true')
                h3(data-i18n='strengths.item1.title', data-en='Integrated Supply Chain', data-zh='供应链一体化') Integrated Supply Chain
                p(data-i18n='strengths.item1.text', data-en='From raw materials to technical support — every stage coordinated for consistent quality and on-time delivery.', data-zh='从原材料到技术支持，全流程统一管理，确保质量稳定与按时交付。') From raw materials to technical support — every stage coordinated for consistent quality and on-time delivery.
            .home-strength-item
                .home-strength-icon
                    i.fa-solid.fa-shield-halved(aria-hidden='true')
                h3(data-i18n='strengths.item2.title', data-en='Quality You Can Verify', data-zh='可验证的品质保障') Quality You Can Verify
                p(data-i18n='strengths.item2.text', data-en='Strict process controls at every production stage, backed by documented quality management systems.', data-zh='每个生产环节严格管控，以完善的质量管理体系为支撑。') Strict process controls at every production stage, backed by documented quality management systems.
            .home-strength-item
                .home-strength-icon
                    i.fa-solid.fa-headset(aria-hidden='true')
                h3(data-i18n='strengths.item3.title', data-en='Fast, Practical Support', data-zh='快速响应与技术支持') Fast, Practical Support
                p(data-i18n='strengths.item3.text', data-en='Responsive technical and commercial support tailored to real application requirements, not generic answers.', data-zh='针对实际应用需求提供快速响应的技术与商务支持。') Responsive technical and commercial support tailored to real application requirements, not generic answers.
